ce/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taro Daniel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that, if they lose, Murray's last-ever match will not be on the main Court Philippe-Chatrier.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6467063947593978e-37, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe-Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Chatrier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's already set to be an anti-climatic affair when Murray ends his spectacular, 19-year career at the Olympics asthere will be no real send-off for the former world No.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6467063947593978e-37, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Tennis Federation previously explained that they come under IOC guidance, and Olympic bosses do not hold retirement ceremonies.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Tennis Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Tennis_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0044338172750725e-22, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Murray's retirement could have even less fanfare as he has been snubbed from the biggest court at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6467063947593978e-37, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those in charge of the schedule have already shown that high-profile doubles matches can get top billing on Chatrier asRafael NadalandCarlos Alcarazfaced Maximo Gonzalez and Andres Molteni in the 15,000-strong stadium on Saturday night.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"score\": 0.9999999983701855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maximo Gonzalez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped